    ScannableTable, StreamableTable, Table, Wrapper

    public class CsvStreamScannableTable
extends CsvScannableTable
implements StreamableTable
    Table based on a CSV file.

    It implements the ScannableTable interface, so Calcite gets data by calling the scan(DataContext) method.
